pull.title: Stricter BIP32 decoding and test vector 5
pull.body: This adds detection for various edge cases when decoding BIP32 extended pubkeys/privkeys, and tests them using the proposed https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/pull/921 BIP32 test vector 5.

issue.title: added test vector #5 for invalid extended keys
issue.body: The BIP32 specification lacks test vectors for invalid extended keys that should not be parsed as valid. Such test vectors are proposed here.
